Nana Visitor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nana_Visitor 0 Nana Tucker ( nə-NAH; born July 26, 1957), known professionally as Nana Visitor, is an American actress, known for playing Kira Nerys in the television series Star Trek: Deep Space Nine and Jean Ritter in the television series Wildfire.
